{"id":96,"parent_id":80,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":96,"title":"Mosiah 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mosiah","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","God redeems men from their lost and fallen state—Those who are carnal remain as though there were no redemption—Christ brings to pass a resurrection to endless life or to endless damnation. About 148",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.1","order":"05.19.016.10187"},["b","1"],"And now, it came to pass that after Abinadi had spoken these words he stretched forth his hand and said: The time shall come when all shall see the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"salvation"],"of the Lord; when",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"every"],"nation, kindred, tongue, and people shall see eye to eye and shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"confess"],"before God that his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"judgments"],"are just."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.2","order":"05.19.016.10188"},["b","2"],"And then shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"wicked"],"be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"cast out"],", and they shall have cause to howl, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"weep"],", and wail, and gnash their teeth; and this because they would not",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"hearken"],"unto the voice of the Lord; therefore the Lord redeemeth them not."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3","order":"05.19.016.10189"},["b","3"],"For they are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"carnal"],"and devilish, and the devil has power over them; yea, even that old serpent that did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"beguile"],"our first parents, which was the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"cause"],"of their fall; which was the cause of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"all"],"mankind becoming carnal, sensual, devilish,",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_3e"},"knowing"],"evil from good,",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_3f"},"subjecting"],"themselves to the devil."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.4","order":"05.19.016.10190"},["b","4"],"Thus all mankind were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"lost"],"; and behold, they would have been endlessly lost were it not that God redeemed his people from their lost and fallen state."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.5","order":"05.19.016.10191"},["b","5"],"But remember that he that persists in his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"carnal"],"nature, and goes on in the ways of sin and rebellion against God, remaineth in his fallen state and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"devil"],"hath all power over him. Therefore he is as though there was no",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"redemption"],"made, being an enemy to God; and also is the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"devil"],"an enemy to God."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.6","order":"05.19.016.10192"},["b","6"],"And now if Christ had not come into the world, speaking of things to come",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"as"],"though they had already come, there could have been no redemption."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.7","order":"05.19.016.10193"},["b","7"],"And if Christ had not risen from the dead, or have broken the bands of death that the grave should have no victory, and that death should have no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"sting"],", there could have been no resurrection."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.8","order":"05.19.016.10194"},["b","8"],"But there is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"resurrection"],", therefore the grave hath no victory, and the sting of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"death"],"is swallowed up in Christ."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.9","order":"05.19.016.10195"},["b","9"],"He is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"light"],"and the life of the world; yea, a light that is endless, that can never be darkened; yea, and also a life which is endless, that there can be no more death."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.10","order":"05.19.016.10196"},["b","10"],"Even this mortal shall put on",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"immortality"],", and this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"corruption"],"shall put on incorruption, and shall be brought to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"stand"],"before the bar of God, to be judged of him according to their works whether they be good or whether they be evil—"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.11","order":"05.19.016.10197"},["b","11"],"If they be good, to the resurrection of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"endless"],"life and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"happiness"],"; and if they be evil, to the resurrection of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"endless"],"damnation, being delivered up to the devil, who hath subjected them, which is damnation—"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.12","order":"05.19.016.10198"},["b","12"],"Having gone according to their own carnal wills and desires; having never called upon the Lord while the arms of mercy were extended towards them; for the arms of mercy were extended towards them, and they would",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"not"],"; they being warned of their iniquities and yet they would not depart from them; and they were commanded to repent and yet they would not repent."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.13","order":"05.19.016.10199"},["b","13"],"And now, ought ye not to tremble and repent of your sins, and remember that only in and through Christ ye can be saved?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.14","order":"05.19.016.10200"},["b","14"],"Therefore, if ye teach the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"law"],"of Moses, also teach that it is a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"shadow"],"of those things which are to come—"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.15","order":"05.19.016.10201"},["b","15"],"Teach them that redemption cometh through Christ the Lord, who is the very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Eternal Father"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.1a","order":"05.19.016.10202"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"TG Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.1b","order":"05.19.016.10204"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.20.20-21"},"Mosiah 3:20 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.1c","order":"05.19.016.10206"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.31"},"Mosiah 27:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.104"},"D&C 88:104"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.1d","order":"05.19.016.10208"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.2a","order":"05.19.016.10210"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/91.8"},"Ps. 91:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/12.1"},"Jer. 12:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.9.9-10"},"D&C 1:9 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.2b","order":"05.19.016.10212"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/52.5"},"Ps. 52:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.54"},"D&C 63:54"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.2c","order":"05.19.016.10214"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.42.41-42"},"Matt. 13:42 (41–42)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/13.28"},"Luke 13:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.13"},"Alma 40:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.22"},"Moses 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.2d","order":"05.19.016.10216"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.16"},"Jer. 44:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/11.13"},"Ether 11:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3a","order":"05.19.016.10218"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/5.19.16-26"},"Gal. 5:19 (16–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.19"},"Mosiah 3:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3b","order":"05.19.016.10220"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/3.13"},"Gen. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.9"},"2 Ne. 9:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/8.25"},"Ether 8:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.19.5-19"},"Moses 4:19 (5–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3c","order":"05.19.016.10222"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.13"},"Moses 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3d","order":"05.19.016.10224"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/14.3"},"Ps. 14:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"3e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3e","order":"05.19.016.10226"},["b","3e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/3.5"},"Gen. 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.18.18,26"},"2 Ne. 2:18 (18, 26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/29.5"},"Alma 29:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.16.15-19"},"Moro. 7:16 (15–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.3f","order":"05.19.016.10228"},["b","3f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.41.41-42"},"Alma 5:41 (41–42)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.40"},"D&C 29:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.4a","order":"05.19.016.10230"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.7"},"2 Ne. 9:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.45"},"Alma 11:45"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.36"},"12:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.6.6,9,14"},"42:6 (6, 9, 14)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fall-of-man"},"TG Fall of Man"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.5a","order":"05.19.016.10232"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/carnal-mind"},"TG Carnal Mind"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.5b","order":"05.19.016.10234"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"TG Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.5c","order":"05.19.016.10236"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.6"},"1 Ne. 10:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.6.5-8"},"2 Ne. 2:6 (5–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.20"},"25:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.22.22-25"},"Alma 12:22 (22–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.5d","order":"05.19.016.10238"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.6a","order":"05.19.016.10240"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.26.24-27"},"2 Ne. 25:26 (24–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jarom/1.11"},"Jarom 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.13"},"Mosiah 3:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.7a","order":"05.19.016.10242"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.14"},"Hosea 13:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.8.8,20"},"Mosiah 15:8 (8, 20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.8a","order":"05.19.016.10244"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.10"},"2 Ne. 9:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.15.6-15"},"Alma 42:15 (6–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.8b","order":"05.19.016.10246"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/25.8"},"Isa. 25:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.54-55"},"1 Cor. 15:54–55"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/7.5"},"Morm. 7:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.9a","order":"05.19.016.10248"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.14"},"Ether 3:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.18"},"Moro. 7:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.13.7-13"},"D&C 88:13 (7–13)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-light-of-the-world"},"TG Jesus Christ, Light of the World"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.10a","order":"05.19.016.10250"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.2"},"Alma 40:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/immortality"},"TG Immortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.10b","order":"05.19.016.10252"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.42"},"1 Cor. 15:42"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.10c","order":"05.19.016.10254"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.4"},"3 Ne. 26:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.11a","order":"05.19.016.10256"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/12.2.2-3"},"Dan. 12:2 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.29.28-29"},"John 5:29 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.11b","order":"05.19.016.10258"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.11c","order":"05.19.016.10260"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/9.11"},"Alma 9:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/damnation"},"TG Damnation"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.12a","order":"05.19.016.10262"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.14a","order":"05.19.016.10264"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.14b","order":"05.19.016.10266"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.31"},"Mosiah 13:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.15.15-16"},"Alma 25:15 (15–16)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/16.15a","order":"05.19.016.10268"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.8"},"Mosiah 3:8"],"."]]}
